<P><B>MESASIMULIUM</B> Zhang, 1986b: 81. Type species: <I>Mesasimulium lahaigouense</I>
Zhang, 1986, by original designation.<BR>
<B>lahaigouense</B> Zhang, 1986b: 81. PA: China (Upper Jurassic) [C].<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<P><CENTER>Genus <B>SIMULIMIMA</B> Kalugina</CENTER>
<P><B>SIMULIMIMA</B> Kalugina in Kalugina &amp; Kovalev, 1985: 43. Type
species: <I>Simulimima grandis</I> Kalugina, 1985, by original designation.<BR>
<B>grandis</B> Kalugina <I>in</I> Kalugina &amp; Kovalev, 1985: 44. PA:
Russia (Siberia) (Lower/Middle Jurassic) [C].<BR>
